<l>kuṟikkoṇṭu nōkkāmai yallā lorukaṇ</l>
<l>ciṟakkaṇittāḷ pōla nakum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>She not only avoids a direct look at me, but looks as it were with a half-closed eye and smiles.</l>
